Sec. 60.024. ADDITIONAL NOTICE OF PUBLIC HEARING. In addition
to other notice required by law, before the 14th day before the date
of the public hearing, notice of the hearing shall be mailed to the
persons who signed the petition and be published in a newspaper with
general circulation in the county with the most land within the
proposed district.
Added by Acts 2001, 77th Leg., ch. 1393, Sec. 1, eff. June 16, 2001.

